&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p id="aMnFB7"&gt;The &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/5/2/23708385/bluesky-weather-report-moderation-app-store"&gt;Bluesky app&lt;/a&gt; looks and functions a lot like X, but it’s a decentralized social media platform that’s...&lt;/p&gt;
